		<br>
		<p>Our projects experience includes commissioning many 25kV primary sub-stations. Working in parallel with equipment vendor specialists we provide supervisory, validation and coordination services for these types of installations.</p>

		<p>
			Our typical services for these project include: 
			<ul>
				<li>Review of contractual obligation between the Owner and vendor and contractors in relation to functional acceptance tests requirements and procedures, operators training, systems documentation and turn over acceptance criteria’s</li>
				<li>Development of the installation commissioning plan and project commissioning schedule</li>
				<li>Acting as the Owner’s representative during the construction stage, witnessing progress of installation and site testing</li>
				<li>Development of pre-function and functional test check sheets</li>
				<li>Pre-functional tests include installation validation for all equipment, sensors and instrumentation, as well as full PLC input/output checks</li>
				<li>Systems activation check sheets include owner's installation and operational requirements, as well as regulatory authority reviews and approvals</li>
				<li>Witnessing of functional testing. Functional testing included operation validation at a system-wide level, rather than individual components</li>
				<li>Reviewing of the Operation and Equipment manuals provided by the contractors.  These documents were reviewed with respect to the owner's requirements, as well as adequacy and completeness for operating and maintaining the plant</li>
				<li>Acting as Owner’s training coordinator for facility operations and maintenance personnel scheduling and overseeing all aspects of training throughout the commissioning, turnover, and acceptance phases. Developed training agendas in cooperation with facility contractor and Owner’s facility group. Training activities included a focus on safety, operation, maintenance, preventative maintenance, troubleshooting, and analysis of the plant</li>
				<li>Preparing a comprehensive summary commissioning report</li>
			</ul>
